Game Plan
1, Client opens the site and is automatically added if there is another client waiting, else that client goes into waiting state.
2, After displaying the basic rules dialog box, and informing which side the client is playing. The game starts
3, At start there will be one unit for each of the client with 10 tanks each.
4, Every 2 seconds a new tank is generated in every unit except the neutral unit.
5, To kill one enemy tank we need one tank but both of them gets destroyed.
6, To gain a UNIT you need to have at least one tank inside.
7, First team to conquer all units win the battle 
